text: Dichostates quadrisignatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Hintz in 1912. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Dichostates quadrisignatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1912
